ias","date":"August 21, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Sufyan reported: Wahb ibn Munabbih, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, in the wisdom of the household of David it is written that it is a duty upon a wise person to not neglect four moments: a time in which to privately converse with one\u2019s Lord Almighty, a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/23\/ibn-sireen-biggest-sinners\/","url_meta":{"origin":25140,"position":1},"title":"Ibn Sirin on Sin: Biggest sinners mention other people\u2019s sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn Hassan reported: Muhammad ibn Sirin, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWe used to say that people with the most faults are the quickest of them to mention the faults of others.\u201d Source: al-S\u0323amt li Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 138 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0647\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064e\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25138,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/09\/abu-saeed-silence-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":25140,"position":2},"title":"Abu Sa\u2019id on Silence: By silence you will overcome the Devil","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Aqil ibn Mudrik reported: A man said to Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cAdvise me.\u201d Abu Sa\u2019id said, \u201cYou must be silent except in the truth, for by it you will defeat Satan.\u201d Source: al-\u1e62amt li Ibn Ab\u012b Duny\u0101 91 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0642\u064a\u0644 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u062f\u0631\u0643 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064b\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25386,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/05\/ali-silence-ilm\/","url_meta":{"origin":25140,"position":3},"title":"Ali on &#8216;Ilm: No good in silence on beneficial knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Razi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThere is no good in silence when it comes to knowledge, just as there is no good in speaking when it comes to ignorance.\u201d Source: al-Tafsi\u0304r al-Kabi\u0304r 2:30 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0627\u0632\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33832,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/12\/10\/umar-silence-some-falsehood\/","url_meta":{"origin":25140,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Silence: Some falsehood is defeated by ignoring it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Yusuf reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cKnow that Allah has servants who cause some falsehood to die out by ignoring it and they give life to the truth by mentioning it.\u201d Source: Kita\u0304b al-Kharra\u0304j 1\/23 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u064a\u0648\u0633\u0641 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35377,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/10\/speak-good-silent-safe\/","url_meta":{"origin":25140,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Silence: Speak good and be rewarded, be silent and safe","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 10, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSpeak what is good and acquire gains, or refrain from speaking evil and be safe.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Shihab al-Qud\u0323a\u0304\u02bbi\u0304 666 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u062a\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u06